# Trivy vulnerability ignore list for argus-mcp
# Format: one CVE ID per line

# CVE-2026-34040 — github.com/docker/docker v28.5.2+incompatible
# Fixed in Docker Engine v29.3.1, but v29.x is NOT published as a Go module.
# The Go module proxy only has up to v28.5.2+incompatible. We cannot upgrade
# until Docker publishes v29.x to the Go module registry.
# Component: tools/docker-adapter (gobinary)
# Reviewed: 2026-04-06
CVE-2026-34040

# CVE-2026-33671 — picomatch 4.0.3 (fixed in 4.0.4, 3.0.2, 2.3.2)
# This is an npm dependency bundled in the base Debian image's Node.js/npm
# installation (/usr/lib/node_modules/npm/node_modules/picomatch). We do not
# use npm or picomatch — it ships with the base image and is outside our
# control. Only affects the standard image (not DHI/Chainguard).
# Reviewed: 2026-04-06
CVE-2026-33671
